{"id":99,"ayahs":[{"number":128,"arabic":"وَإِنِ ٱمْرَأَةٌ خَافَتْ مِنۢ بَعْلِهَا نُشُوزًا أَوْ إِعْرَاضًۭا فَلَا جُنَاحَ عَلَيْهِمَآ أَن يُصْلِحَا بَيْنَهُمَا صُلْحًۭا ۚ وَٱلصُّلْحُ خَيْرٌۭ ۗ وَأُحْضِرَتِ ٱلْأَنفُسُ ٱلشُّحَّ ۚ وَإِن تُحْسِنُوا۟ وَتَتَّقُوا۟ فَإِنَّ ٱللَّهَ كَانَ بِمَا تَعْمَلُونَ خَبِيرًۭا","translation":"And if a woman has reason to fear ill-treat­ment from her husband, or that he might turn away from her, it shall not be wrong for the two to set things peacefully to rights between themselves: for peace is best, and selfishness is ever-present in human souls. But if you do good and are conscious of Him - behold, God is indeed aware of all that you do.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/621.mp3","surahId":4,"words":[{"id":77723,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِنِ","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/004_128_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77724,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱمْرَأَةٌ","translation":"কোন স্ত্রী","audioUrl":"wbw/004_128_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77725,"position":3,"arabic":"خَافَتْ","translation":"ভয় করে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_128_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77726,"position":4,"arabic":"مِنۢ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_128_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77727,"position":5,"arabic":"بَعْلِهَا","translation":"তার স্বামীর","audioUrl":"wbw/004_128_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77728,"position":6,"arabic":"نُشُوزًا","translation":"দুর্ব্যবহারের","audioUrl":"wbw/004_128_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77729,"position":7,"arabic":"أَوْ","translation":"বা","audioUrl":"wbw/004_128_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77730,"position":8,"arabic":"إِعْرَاضًۭا","translation":"উপেক্ষার","audioUrl":"wbw/004_128_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77731,"position":9,"arabic":"فَلَا","translation":"নাই তবে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_128_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77732,"position":10,"arabic":"جُنَاحَ","translation":"কোন দোষ","audioUrl":"wbw/004_128_010.mp3","c